rforming a parameter scan, we obtained the class of\neffective potentials that lead to FOPT scenarios that can be probed by SKA\nthrough pulsar timing and GW observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 04:36:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-21"}
