pen innovations in diagnostics for providing high\nquality medical care in low and medium resource settings. Combined with rise of\n3D printing, Inkwell presents an alternative to traditional centralized\nmanufacturing and opens up distributed manufacturing of medical diagnostics in\nglobal context.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 10:41:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-21"}
