e of a linear shear flow. The\nproposed correlations for the drag, lift and torque coefficients can be used in\nlarge-scale simulations performed in the Eulerian-Lagrangian framework with\nlocally uniform and non-uniform flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 14:53:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-21"}
