 Nambu-Goto action leads to an equation for entanglement entropies\nin the boundary theory of the form of a Toda equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 15:25:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-21"}
